		"Id": "mechdef_banshee_BNC-3O",
		"Name": "Banshee",
		"Details": "The Oberon Confederation needed new designs for their war machine against the Rim Worlds Republic and the Clan forces in their region of the Inner Sphere and so turned to the old standby, the Banshee, for inspiration. Out of their factories came this, the BNC-3O. Armed with a trio of the Oberon Confederation's new Pepperbox Rifles as well as a battery of Medium and Small Chemical Lasers, the BNC-3O has a surprisingly hard initial punch that's backed up by plenty of Heavy Plating Armor for sustainability. The Oberons built the -3O with their Cobbled-Together Reinforced structure, giving the -3O even more durability in combat. The BNC-3O doesn't hit the hardest but it's in the fight for a long, long time, making it a threat even to Clan garrison forces.",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_banshee"
